# Unified Demo Configuration

## Required: JWT_SECRET

Agent ROS Bridge requires JWT authentication for security.

### Generate a secure secret:

```bash
export JWT_SECRET=$(openssl rand -base64 32)
```

### Or create a .env file:

```bash
echo "JWT_SECRET=$(openssl rand -base64 32)" > .env
```

## Security Warning

⚠️ **Never use default or weak JWT secrets in production!**

The bridge will fail to start without a valid JWT_SECRET.

## Running the Demo

```bash
# Option 1: Export variable
export JWT_SECRET=$(openssl rand -base64 32)
docker-compose up

# Option 2: Use .env file (after creating it above)
docker-compose up
```
